title: DomainHolder
shortDescription: Easily park and sell your domain.
longDescription:
## Let your unused domains sell themselves

Set up a "for sale" page on your unused domain names in 15 seconds. Visitors will be able to see your domains price, and leave a message for you if they're interested.

Your parking page can be hosted at the root of your site, or on a subdomain if you are looking to also use the site for another purpose.
author: DomainHolder.io
